{"tid":1564843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際文宣] 香港又有一班人好努力咁做文宣：今次係走出香港，向世界各地既人講香港人既故事！","createTime":"2019-09-13T02:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T03:16:46.000Z","uid":78276,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"459f36567e2c53e1110e4788bf182994f040981c","tid":1564843,"uid":78276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"香港又有一班人好努力咁做文宣：今次係走出香港，向世界各地既人講香港人既故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1S74n3z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1S74n3z.jpg&h=ca27e83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vijN5gU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvijN5gU.jpg&h=233072ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個反送中運動話咁快就過左3個月，你有冇d咩想同香港人講，甚至分享俾<span style=\"color: red;\">外國既朋友</span>知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;We Are HKers我地係香港人&quot;係參考<span style=\"color: red;\">Humans of New York</span>既成功例子，希望透過網站同各大社交平台，將<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人既故事</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">感受</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">對未來的盼望</span>宣揚開去。<br />\n<br />\n點解要咁做?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為我地熱愛香港!</span> 我地想紀錄低我地係鏡頭後一幕幕鮮為人知既小故事，同時更想為一路付出既大家打打氣。<br />\n<br />\n而特別係外國，大多數人都只係透過<span style=\"color: red;\">新聞</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">社交媒體</span>而知道香港發生咩事。但往往亦因為硬新聞(hard news)既限制，好多外國人都唔清楚我地既不論勇武定和理非一直上街表達五大訴求背後既原因，甚或係點解我地要將武力升級，係都要同中共政府抗衡等等。就因為咁，佢地都未必能夠完全明白同表態支持，或者有部分<span style=\"color: red;\">外國人甚至覺得我地做多左，而做咁多野都會係得不償失。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我地唔係! 我地唔可以停落黎，因為呢個係一場<span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span>! 面對佢地既質疑同不諒解，我地唔應該停，反而係更應該做更多野去等佢地明白，感染佢地!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左得到更多人既支持同體諒，我地決定開個平台，<span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎大家分享一下發夢、行街，甚至係日常生活既小故事。</span>我地會將內容翻譯成英文(甚至多國語言)，等多d人可以更全面了解香港人既生活現況同核心價值，仲有對未來既盼望。<br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐，當然想大家支持下我地啦! 請follow我地各個page，有稿投稿，有意見就隨時搵我地! Share埋俾你身邊既friends!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wearehkers.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wearehkers.com%2F&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=78b02ccf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wearehkers.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n想幫手既，以下既位等緊你! 請填好表格，我地會盡快聯絡你!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔹Journalist (source / interview / write, etc.)<br />\n🔹English -&gt; Chinese Translator<br />\n🔹Chinese -&gt; English Translator<br />\n🔹Designer/Artist<br />\n🔹Photographer<br />\n🔹Public/Media Relations + Marketing<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/9Q2og9jxEqx7hitUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F9Q2og9jxEqx7hitUA&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=a531e403\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/9Q2og9jxEqx7hitUA</a><br />\n<br />\n投稿/聯絡: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wearehkers.com/contact / contact@wearehkers.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wearehkers.com%2Fcontact%20%2F%20contact%40wearehkers.com&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=89514268\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wearehkers.com/contact / contact@wearehkers.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>總之，我地係香港人，香港人加油!!!</strong>"},{"pid":"b95092e6a9af8db65c0dfab350d00b1c98a4a032","tid":1564843,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:26:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4b144db534793621fc48f2fb2a42599ea0605d7","tid":1564843,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:26:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></st